{"tid":2514483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"患有ADHD青年管有一支觀星筆一把摺刀 官以入獄1年作量刑起點","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T09:45:03.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91f24b738ef4e73ff46c7e71544ae8d3baad5534","tid":2514483,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=94619938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&h=fd68db83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方前年11月派駐重兵包圍理工大學，大批示威者被困。患有過度活躍症的年輕興趣班導師試圖離開時遭警截停，搜出摺刀及雷射筆等物件。他早前承認一項管有攻擊性武器罪，主任裁判官嚴舜儀今在九龍城法院判刑時指，被告原本攜同涉案物品到理大煮飯，惟離開時將物品變成自衞武器；當時環境混亂，若他在這情況下使用武器，會對潛在人身傷害造成極大風險，判他即時入獄8個月。"},{"pid":"56f4f72417a0d9c6e3142c675fd87e3628ffcbd4","tid":2514483,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f24b738ef4e73ff46c7e71544ae8d3baad5534","tid":2514483,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=94619938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&h=fd68db83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方前年11月派駐重兵包圍理工大學，大批示威者被困。患有過度活躍症的年輕興趣班導師試圖離開時遭警截停，搜出摺刀及雷射筆等物件。他早前承認一項管有攻擊性武器罪，主任裁判官嚴舜儀今在九龍城法院判刑時指，被告原本攜